== About me
I'm a Postdoc at [https://sky.cs.berkeley.edu/ Sky Computing Lab], UC Berkeley, working with [http://people.eecs.berkeley.edu/~istoica/ Prof. Ion Stoica]. I earned my PhD from UC San Diego, under the supervision of [https://swanson.ucsd.edu/ Prof. Steven Swanson]. My main research interests span memory and storage management, programming models, distributed systems, and their intersections. Recently, I've been focusing on GPU and LLM memory management. 



